owl:Ontology.terms:description: An ontology representing covariates for the ENIGMA Suicidal Thoughts and Behaviors working group
owl:Ontology.terms:title: The STB Ontology

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Subject's age in years .
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: age

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the Behavioral Activation System subscale score on the BIS/BAS is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: BAS total score

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the age of onset of the subject's Bipolar Disorder is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: BD age of onset

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject currently has Bipolar Disorder.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: BD current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the subject's current Bipolar Disorder state (ie: depressed, hypomanic, manic, eutyhmic, mixed)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: BD current state

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the subject's Bipolar Disorder type (ie: type I, type II, NOS, no BD, NA) is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: BD diagnosis type

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject had Bipolar Disorder during their lifetime.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: BD lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the subject's current Bipolar Disorder stage (first episode, recurrent episodes, no BD, and NA = no information available) is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: BD stage

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the Behavioral Inhibition System subscale score on the BIS/BAS is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: BIS total score

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the subject's Global Clinical Impression Scale's total score.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: CGI total

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if age of onset of subject's Generalized Anxiety Disorder is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: GAD age of onset

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject currently has Generalized Anxiety Disorder.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: GAD current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether if the subject had Generalized Anxiety Disorder during their lifetime is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: GAD lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject's Global Assessment of Functioning scale total score is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: GAF total

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The IQ scale used for each subject/group (ie: WISC-IV, WAIS-IV, WASI-II).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: IQ method

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the age of onset of the subject's first depressive episode is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: MDD age of onset

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject currently has Major Depressive Disorder.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: MDD current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject had Major Depressive Disorder during their lifetime.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: MDD lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the current stage of the subject's Major Depressive Disorder (ie: recurrent or first episode) is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: MDD stage

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the subject's current number of depressive episodes is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: MDD total episodes

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Property which states whether subject's marital status (ie: single, married) is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: marital status

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the age of onset of the subject's Obsessive Compulsive Disorder is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: OCD age of onset

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject currently has Obsessive Compulsive Disorder.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: OCD current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject had Obsessive Compulsive Disorder during their lifetime.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: OCD lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Property which states whether subject's occupation is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: occupation

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the age of onset of the subject's Post-Traumatic Stress Disorder is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: PTSD age of onset

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject currently has Post-Traumatic Stress Disorder.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: PTSD current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject had Post-Traumatic Stress Disorder during their lifetime.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: PTSD lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the subject's Social and Occupational Functioning Assessment Scale total score is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: SOFAS total

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Property to state whether subject's sex (male, female, other) is specified or not.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: sex

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Property which states whether the identification code/number of unique subjects is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: subject ID

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the scale used to determine the diagnosis of alcohol use disorder (ie: SCID, ASSIST, AUDIT) is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: alcohol use disorder scale

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the age of onset of the subject's alcohol use disorder.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: alcohol use disorder age of onset

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the subject's current alcohol use disorder (ie: dependence, abuse, none).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: alcohol use disorder current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the subject's previous lifetime alcohol use disorder (ie: dependence, abuse, none) is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: alcohol use disorder lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject's use of antidepressants at time of scan is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: antidepressant use current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject's use of antidepressants during their lifetime is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: antidepressant use lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the subject's use of antiepileptics at time of scan is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: antiepileptic use current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the subject's use of antiepileptics during their lifetime is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: antiepileptic use lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject's use of 2nd generation (atypical) antipsychotics at time of scan is speciied.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: atypical antipsychotic use current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject's use of 2nd generation (atypical) antipsychotics during their lifetime is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: atypical antipsychotic use lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject's Barratt Impulsiveness Scale total score is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: barratt total score

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the Barratt Impulsiveness Scale version that was used.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: barratt version used

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: any demographic property
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: demographic property

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Property which states whether the diagnostic group each subject is associated with (control vs. experimental) is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: diagnosis group

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Subject's education coded as categories (ie: a range from 1-5)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: education category

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The method used for coding the Education Category (ie: 1 = some high school, 2 = some college, 3 = some professional degree)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: education method

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Property to state whether subject's education in years is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: education years

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject's use of lithium at time of scan is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: lithium use current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject's use of lithium during their lifetime is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: lithium use lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Any Medication use/Somatic Health property
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Medication use/Somatic Health property

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the number of negative life events the subject experienced in the past 6 months is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: negative life events

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the questionnaire/interview used to assess negative life events from past 6 months (e.g. NLESS, SLESQ).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: negative life events method

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if age of onset of subject's other psychiatric disorders is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: other Dx age of onset

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the subject's other psychiatric diagnoses at the time of scan (e.g. borderline personality disorder, ADHD, etc.).
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: other dx current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the subject's other psychiatric diagnoses during their lifetime (e.g. borderline personality disorder, ADHD, etc.)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: other dx lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the subject's other medication use at time of scan.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: other medication use current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the subject's other medication use during their lifetime.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: other medication use lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether age of onset of subject's substance use disorder is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: other substance use disorder age of onset

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes subject's current drug use that meets criteria for substance abuse disorder at the time of scan (e.g. cocaine, opiods etc.)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: other substance use disorder current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes subject's previous lifetime drug use that meets criteria for lifetime substance abuse disorder (e.g. cocaine, opiods etc.)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: other substance use disorder lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether age of onset of subject's Panic Disorder is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: panic disorder age of onset

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject currently has Panic Disorder.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: panic disorder current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject had Panic Disorder during their lifetime.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: panic disorder lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Highest level of parental socioeconomic status either based on education, occupation or both.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: parent socioeconomic status

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The scale used in measuring a parent(s) socioeconomic status.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: parent socioeconomic status scale

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Any psychopathological property
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: psychopathological property

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the age of onset of the subject's psychotic disorder is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: psychotic disorder age of onset

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject currently has a Psychotic Disorder.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: pyschotic disorder current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the subject's Psychotic Disorder type (ie: schizophrenia, schizoaffective disorder, delusional disorder, psychosis NOS, schizophreniform disorder, brief psychotic disorder, shared psychotic disorder, substance-induced psychosis) is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: psychotic disorder diagnosis type

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject had the Psychotic Disorder during their lifetime.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: pyschotic disorder lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Subject's race/ethnicity.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: race ethnicity

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Any score property
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: score property

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject is currently smoking.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: smoking status current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject smoked during their lifetime.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: smoking status lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether age of onset of subject's Social Anxiety Disorder is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: social anxiety disorder age of onset

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject currently has Social Anxiety Disorder.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: social anxiety disorder current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject had Social Anxiety Disorder during their lifetime.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: social anxiety disorder lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject has a type of somatic illness.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: somatic illness current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the subject's somatic illness type.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: somatic illness type

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The scale used in measuring a subject’s socioeconomic status.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: subject socioeconomic status

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The highest level of subject's socioeconomic status based on education, occupation or both.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: subject socioeconomic status

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the subject's use of 1st generation (typical) antipsychotics at time of scan is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: typical antipsychotic use current

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the subject's use of 1st generation (typical) antipsychotics during their lifetime is specified.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: typical antipsychotic use lifetime

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Any use disorder property
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: use disorder property

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A class used to describe covariates information for a cohort or study.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Covariates
